5:
Hello? We're here to deliver a letter
from the Guild.
9:
*yawn* Morning, Alk. You need my
signature or anything?
13:
We're not with the post office, so no.
Here you go.
16:
Are you just getting up now, Subaru?
That's one serious case of bedhead.
20:
Yeah, I'm house sitting today, so I
ended up sleeping in a little too late...
25:
If you have that much time on your
hands, you'd do well to go out for a
stroll.
29:
You say that, but I don't exactly
know the hot spots in Palpebra.
32:
You two have any plans after this? If
not, wanna join me for a little
adventure?
34:
What's it called again? The Callie
Scope? I've been meaning to check
it out.
39:
Huh? Isn't that where you got
kidnapped to? Are you sure?
43:
It's not like I can avoid it, especially if
we're gonna try to make a living
here. I gotta get a grasp on the
place, and fast!
45:
You've been there a ton of times,
right? You guys are practically
veterans!
49:
So please, I'm begging you! Just this
once! Pleeease?
53:
Whoa! Now that's some serious
power! You blew those guys away
like it was nothing.
57:
Hey, why the hell am I stuck
babysitting the brat too?
61:
Well, the more guards, the better,
right? Especially since the
kidnapping happened pretty
recently...
65:
Yeah, well... You'd think he'd be more
careful after that, but he's acting like
this is a field trip...
70:
Let's go, Subaru. Try not to stray too
far from us, okay?
75: Okay! Don't you worry about me!
79: A jewel? Did somebody drop it?
89:
Man, that smarts! Who the hell puts
a trap door—
92:
Wait, where am I? Something tells
me I better tread lightly...
99:
C-crap, you scared me, little buddy!
I thought you were a monster for a
second there...
102:
It's dangerous here, you know. Why
don't you come here, and I'll take
you back to tow—
113:
Alk! Light! Nimbus! Somebody, help
me!
122: (No... I don't... want to die here...)
130:
I'll buy us some time! Wake the kid
up NOW!
133: Subaru, come on, get it together!
157:
You almost DIED back there, you
nitwit! Do you understand?!
160:
I-I'm sorry... I didn't mean to make
light of it...
165:
Subaru, I understand the thrill an
adventure can bring, but you must
understand that we may not always
arrive in time to save you.
166:
You must protect yourself before we
can protect you. If you can't do that,
we won't bring you on any more
expeditions.
169:
As for Nimbus' outburst, please
understand that he's speaking from
experience. He lost a dear friend in
the past.
174:
I'm sorry. I just assumed everything
would be fine as long as Alk and
Nimbus were around.
176:
I really screwed up today. I'll do
better next time.
178:
(I have no idea when death will
show its ugly face. At least that
doesn't change, regardless of what
world I'm in...)
181:
Um... I promise I'll listen to you guys
and be more careful from now on...
So can we still go on adventures
together?
186:
Of course! And you don't have to be
so apologetic. It's not like we're
asking you to listen to EVERYTHING
we say.
192:
We're just telling you to think a little
so you don't end up dead. Got it?
201:
(At this rate, they're gonna be the
ones protecting me all the time.)
203:
(If I want to help Emilia, I need to
change that!)
206: Thanks, guys! I really owe you one!
